  <summary date="2023-08-10T12:41:12Z" status="Introduced in House">Energy Permitting Certainty Act

This bill requires the Department of the Interior to process applications for permits to drill under a valid oil or gas lease even if there are any pending civil actions, provided that the civil actions do not directly affect or involve the application or underlying lease.</summary>
